data.description: Here's the fixer upper you've been looking for. One level home with attached one car garage. Additional slab/foundation where a barn once stood. Has potential to become your new shop or detached garage. Original hardwood under the carpet in all three bedrooms as well as the living room. Large lot in the Centennial school district. Home has newer roof, siding, and windows. Newer electrical, roof and siding all done in 2017. All windows new since 2010. Basement partially finished. Just needs your finishing touches. Roughed in bathroom downstairs.
